<body>
    <div class="sim-card">
        <h1>⚡ 辉光放电仿真 + 🌐 辉光球模拟 <small>自选课题2 · 物理实验教学</small></h1>
        <div class="sub">🔬 平行板辉光放电 | 帕邢定律 · 动态间距 · 放电区域 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 🌀 辉光球：电场驱动等离子丝</div>

        <div class="mode-tabs">
            <button id="modeGlowDischargeBtn" class="mode-btn active">⚛️ 平行板辉光放电</button>
            <button id="modeGlowBallBtn" class="mode-btn">🌐 辉光球 (等离子球)</button>
        </div>

        <div id="dischargeModule">
            <div class="dashboard">
                <div class="control-panel">
                    <div class="param-group">
                        <label>🗲 电压 <i>U</i> <span class="unit-hint">(V)</span></label>
                        <div class="param-row">
                            <input type="range" id="voltageSlider" min="5" max="1200" step="1" value="400">
                            <input type="number" id="voltageInput" min="5" max="1200" step="1" value="400">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-group">
                        <label>🌀 气压 <i>p</i> <span class="unit-hint">(Pa)</span></label>
                        <div class="param-row">
                            <input type="range" id="pressureSlider" min="1" max="800" step="0.5" value="100">
                            <input type="number" id="pressureInput" min="1" max="800" step="0.5" value="100">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-group">
                        <label>📏 电极距离 <i>d</i> <span class="unit-hint">(mm)</span></label>
                        <div class="param-row">
                            <input type="range" id="distanceSlider" min="0.5" max="60" step="0.1" value="5.0">
                            <input type="number" id="distanceInput" min="0.5" max="60" step="0.1" value="5.0">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-group">
                        <label>📐 电极面积 <i>S</i> <span class="unit-hint">(cm²)</span></label>
                        <div class="param-row">
                            <input type="range" id="areaSlider" min="0.5" max="100" step="0.5" value="10">
                            <input type="number" id="areaInput" min="0.5" max="100" step="0.5" value="10">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="param-group">
                        <label>⚛️ 气体种类</label>
                        <select id="gasSelect">
                            <option value="ar">氩气 (Ar) — B=176 V/(cm·Torr), γ≈0.07</option>
                            <option value="air">空气 (Air) — B=365 V/(cm·Torr), γ≈0.01</option>
                            <option value="ne">氖气 (Ne) — B=100 V/(cm·Torr), γ≈0.04</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="formula-box">
                        <div class="formula-title">📐 帕邢定律 — 击穿电压公式（标准形式）</div>
                        <div class="formula-math">
                            $$V_b = \frac{B \cdot p \cdot d}{\ln\left(\frac{A \cdot p \cdot d}{\ln\left(1 + \frac{1}{\gamma}\right)}\right)}$$
                        </div>
                        <div class="formula-detail" id="paschenFormulaDetails">
                            <strong>当前参数：</strong>A=<span id="paramA">12.0</span> (cm·Torr)⁻¹, B=<span id="paramB">176</span>
                            V/(cm·Torr), γ=<span id="paramGamma">0.07</span><br>
                            pd = <span id="pdValue">0.0375</span> Torr·cm &nbsp;|&nbsp;
                            击穿电压 V<sub>b</sub> = <strong id="paschenVinline">---</strong> V
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="status-card">
                        <div style="font-weight:600;">🔌 放电阶段</div>
                        <div class="discharge-state" id="dischargeStateLabel">🔴 未击穿 / 暗放电</div>
                        <div class="status-row">
                            <span>📉 击穿电压 <strong id="paschenV">---</strong> V</span>
                            <span>⚡ 电流 <strong id="simCurrent">0.00</strong> A</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="status-row" style="margin-top:4px;">
                            <span>📊 电流密度 <strong id="currentDensity">0.00</strong> A/cm²</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="btn-row">
                        <button id="resetBtn" class="secondary">⟳ 默认参数</button>
                        <button id="presetStandardBtn" class="preset-btn">📋 标准实验条件</button>
