                    </div>
                    <div class="legend">
                        <span>🟤 阿斯顿暗区</span> <span>🟠 阴极辉区</span> <span>⚫ 克鲁克斯暗区</span>
                        <span>✨ 负辉区</span> <span>🔵 法拉第暗区</span> <span>🌀 正柱区</span> <span>🟢 阳极区</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 12px;" class="iv-canvas-wrapper">
                        <canvas id="iVCurveCanvas" width="820" height="370"></canvas>
                        <div class="region-labels">
                            <span>🔹 暗放电区 (A→E)</span>
                            <span>🔹 辉光放电区 (F→H)</span>
                            <span>🔹 电弧放电区 (I→K)</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="glowballModule" style="display: none;">
            <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start;">
                <div class="glowball-container">
                    <canvas id="glowballCanvas" width="400" height="400"></canvas>
                    <div class="glowball-note">
                        ✨ 鼠标在球内移动 → 放电丝追随手指 ✨<br>
                        模拟高频高压电极产生的辐射状等离子体丝
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="flex:1; min-width:220px; max-width:350px; background:#eef2f7; border-radius:1.5rem; padding:1.2rem;">
                    <h3 style="margin-top:0;font-size:1rem;">🌐 辉光球参数控制</h3>
                    <div style="margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
                        <label style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-weight:600;color:#1f3b4c;margin-bottom:4px;">
                            ⚡ 电压 <span class="param-value" id="glowVoltageVal">80</span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="range" id="glowVoltageSlider" min="20" max="100" step="1" value="80"
                        style="width:100%;cursor:pointer;accent-color:#2c6e9e;">
                        <div style="font-size:0.72rem;color:#6c7e91;">高电压 → 丝更集中，分支更明显</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
                        <label style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-weight:600;color:#1f3b4c;margin-bottom:4px;">
                            🌀 气压 <span class="param-value" id="glowPressureVal">50</span>
                        </label>
